reviews.review_msg: Literally love Dr. Faris so much! I have had about 4 or 5 classes with her as they often fit into my schedule the best. She is always so wonderful and the topics are so interesting. Lots of special topic courses so keep an eye out for possible classes and the title as they change often. She is amazing at giving in depth feedback.

I regret taking her class. Her lesson plans are mixed up. she gives 10 minutes break to students than she herself her 5 min cant control herself to start the class even though she is seeing the students are eating. Also attendence is super mandatory, she hates students who does not go to her class and end up giving them 0.
